<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (whạrnm lyk whạsẖhd lk rby yswʿ
 wsṭ ạlạ̉twn wfy ạlgẖywm hạsbḥk)2
 1- (mhmạ ạ̹n kạn ḥwly ẓlạm wạlʿạlm klh ạ̉tẖạm
 hạsẖhd ʿnk yạ yswʿ whạrnm lyk)2
 2- (bthb ạlryḥ ʿlyạ wtʿly̱ ạlạ̉mwạj ḥwạlyạ
 ạ̉jy fy ḥḍnk yạ fạdyạ wạ̉rnm lyk)2
 3-(rby yswʿ ạlgẖạly fy qrbk tḥlw ạ̉yạmy
 hbny rby dwmạaⁿ ạ̉rnm lyk)2</lyrics>
